{"tid":1397041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"85三罷=支爆按鈕","createTime":"2019-08-02T09:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T19:42:51.000Z","uid":58841,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"094504a0aa7197a65afe07f6829ee5a0b0c49968","tid":1397041,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"只要85成功三罷<br />\n批貨就無辦法趕係侵仔加關稅前去到美國<br />\n咁撚大粒支爆掣係香港<br />\n罷工最多咪無左一日人工<br />\n同支爆相比抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4391bef0d1ba41957533d6d61c8bbdb1d6cdc2","tid":1397041,"uid":25440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"［代發］一群政府新聞主任的公開信<br />\n有職員證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今晚7點中環遮打花園見！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b78f21b64ef70b2f096cf66dc25ca546da07044","tid":1397041,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"義士有生命危險！！8月5號有危險，快入！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392370\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第11頁有藍絲假文宣合集</strong></span><br />\n補番真文宣source<br />\n5/8 全港大三罷+ 7區開🌼 公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/saveinghkgrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsaveinghkgrp&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=c96509b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/saveinghkgrp</a>"},{"pid":"8399cb06bf0733cc2ac484fa5d00d1d930ea3b26","tid":1397041,"uid":271051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:59:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推到支爆</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d5189539b2d577288b667da3670ccba0249fc58","tid":1397041,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推到佢老母支爆</span></span><br />\n一時痛苦換黎一世安寧同自由"},{"pid":"9ec07857415daea1668ffbc88e63e46168574679","tid":1397041,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c57ea169ebb2c62a048e5dbe80e745c02ef67902","tid":1397041,"uid":78913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4e22e63a267010e9c4e93c4c171c64333b14236","tid":1397041,"uid":258328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39957b5e69f3eef12418c98595946b5ebfcab439","tid":1397041,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"下一步該怎樣走？<br />\n<br />\n不要過慮，表面上政府好像以逸待勞，但實情是我們多面的極限施壓已成氣候，習近平和黑天鵝比我們更心急如焚&mdash;&mdash;他們正想利用談判搞散抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n2018年大陸境內債券違約規模達到1200億元，而今年的規模，是5700億元。<br />\n<br />\n59間企業設立的中國民營投資集團，533億元存續債券今年到期。4月首份5億美元債券違約，中建行已硬啃代還3億；另一份5億美元債券，8月2日到期。中民投講到明：還唔到。<br />\n<br />\n今年首6個月，中國企業債務違約金額突破600億。7月15日一天之內有5份債券違約。<br />\n<br />\n7月22日，美國制裁中國神秘石油入口商珠海振戎（北狄改名都衰過人，話明係用來振興伊朗這個西戎）。兩伊戰爭期間，中國向伊朗賣軍火，就是通過這間公司以石油代支。現時進口量佔全國進口量約25%。<br />\n<br />\n2019年有719隻地產債券到期，需要償還的金額達4567億元。2019年至2021三年間，地產企業海外債券到期規模都在200億美元之上。<br />\n<br />\n7月，失業大軍年增超過500萬人。<br />\n<br />\n7月，返鄉潮達740萬人。<br />\n<br />\n7月，特朗普否決將蘋果產品剔出加徵25%關稅的中國貨清單。<br />\n<br />\n7月，惠普、DELL決定將30％筆電生產撤離中國。<br />\n<br />\n7月，山東近百間院校搞農民工「副學士課程」，免考文化試，資格卻與高校畢業生睇齊。<br />\n<br />\n7月，秋行軍蟲和關稅夾擊下，中國多年來首次向俄羅斯入口大豆。<br />\n<br />\n9月，南韓三星將關閉最後一間惠州工廠。美國對300億中國貨品徵10%關稅。<br />\n<br />\n10月26日，美國給予WTO的限期屆滿，WTO必須決定是否將中國、香港和澳門剔出發展中經濟體。<br />\n<br />\n全國心臟病藥脷底丸斷貨，由9蚊暴漲至150蚊一樽。<br />\n<br />\n邊個等得？邊個唔等得？<br />\n<br />\n今日，中美貿易談判在上海重啟，預料實質成果不大。<br />\n<br />\n香港是大陸的後花園，不妨再燒幾把火。<br />\n<br />\n你國家仲有冇糧出啊？"},{"pid":"ac7507fbe234f295dd121e534d165c130664a353","tid":1397041,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d2b35fe71445ab730dae1bd47bb8d3a3350807","tid":1397041,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"不如搞9碼頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去到9月先放貨比佢出"},{"pid":"78f63d50282d20f9ca8be71b8b66c2c9e7fed107","tid":1397041,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"似乎有人仲未明呢樣野係幾咁抵屌"},{"pid":"84510bd44a46d0d8e189cc6f8411755d0c847b1c","tid":1397041,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚侵仔係Twitter講左9月1將剩低300億美金既貨關稅加到25%<br />\n咁個300億而家擺係香港 等緊8月5日出去<br />\n船運最快都要一個月<br />\n即係只要佢個日出唔到去<br />\n支那就仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d089a95bc0c38eb71ce605e38e3b43087720ab","tid":1397041,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8f3591b063e4e9b7c9d77f484f0d0645bce5ad","tid":1397041,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84510bd44a46d0d8e189cc6f8411755d0c847b1c","tid":1397041,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚侵仔係Twitter講左9月1將剩低300億美金既貨關稅加到25%<br />\n咁個300億而家擺係香港 等緊8月5日出去<br />\n船運最快都要一個月<br />\n即係只要佢個日出唔到去<br />\n支那就仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119d27e5e775fbe3fc8f6c301f4d26ced8f1703d","tid":1397041,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"1：五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n2：兄弟爬山，各自努力，齊上齊落。<br />\n3：不割席，不指責，不篤灰。<br />\n4：沒有大台/領導人物。"},{"pid":"710b12442bdc8397340b8a1131bc44230ff70270","tid":1397041,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:42:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}